rComments: Prof Silvey is really sweet and her class was quite easy. It was 85% for 3 essays and 15% for attendance. I honestly didn't do all the readings, just the ones that were necessary for the assignments. She's very well-versed in migration studies so class discussions in GGR198 were really insightful. She also ended class early a lot which is a plus.

She's really approachable and she always tries to engage with the class. 3 short essays, and participation matters. I also had to do a presentation for a participation mark. Take her course if you're interested in politics, gender, and immigration. I'm taking a geography course next semester because of her!
Very helpful and engaging professor who is passionate about her material.
Good Prof, easy and very helpful.

excellent teacher who is engaged with all of the course materials.  Her teaching style is a bit unconventional but it is a rewarding experience if you put in effort and listen to her.  Her class was interesting, fun and she marked very easy.
